snippet.title: My Summer Vacation 3 | Boku no Natsuyasumi 3 | Trailer (PS3 2007)
snippet.description: Boku no Natsuyasumi 3: Kitaguni Hen: Chiisana Boku no Dai Sougen (lit. "My Summer Vacation 3: The Northern Chapter: Little Boku's Big Prairie") is a video game developed by Millennium Kitchen and published by Sony Computer Entertainment for the PlayStation 3. It is part of the popular Boku no Natsuyasumi series and was released in Japan on July 5, 2007.
